WEBVTT

00:04:00.520 --> 00:04:02.760
Wenzangu na mimi
tulichoamua kufanya

00:04:03.600 --> 00:04:06.216
ni kufikiri je tukitumia
mbu wenyewe

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:09.336
kubeba dawa ya wadudu
kutoka sehemu ya chaguo letu

00:04:09.360 --> 00:04:11.256
mpaka kwenye mazingira yao ya kuzaliana

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:14.880
ili mayai yoyote watakayotaga
pale yasiishi.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:18.055
Huyu ni Dickson Lwetoijera.

00:04:18.079 --> 00:04:20.776
Huyu ni mwenzangu
anaeendesha tamasha hili Ifakara.

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:24.056
Na ameonyesha kwa ustadi kua
unaweza kwa kweli kupata mbu

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:26.816
kuja kwenye eneo
ambalo kawaida wanapata damu

00:04:26.840 --> 00:04:30.896
kuchagua kiasi cha
dawa za kusafisha au dawa ya wadudu,